RESOLUTION

HP has made the following updated product kit available to resolve the vulnerabilities. The HP Business Availability Center v8.02 kit is available on the HP Software Support Online portal at: http://support.openview.hp.com/support.jsp .

Software Platform
 BAC v8.02 Patch file name

Solaris
 BAC_00641.zip

Windows
 BAC_00640.zip

Note: This update provides the Apache server v2.2.11

